{"tid":2363468,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求幫推上熱門] 有無發現熱門開始有攻擊signal嘅 post？","createTime":"2021-01-12T08:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T03:37:20.000Z","uid":179645,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc15fe0db02c057460fdd1c4d7d4f8ef7e2ead7","tid":2363468,"uid":179645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:25:15.000Z","msg":"呢段Cm係喺隔離post到Copy出黎<br />\nBy Temuco巴打<br />\n做多一步：改埋WhatsApp狀態<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aHOtkMV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aHOtkMV</a><br />\n#47 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>from a friend 👇<br />\n最近見好多朋友講緊由WhatsApp轉會Signal<br />\n當年，小弟響香港某廣告公司工作<br />\n曾經負責Line嘅網絡宣傳工作<br />\n<br />\n今日想同大家分享一下<br />\n當年我接觸到嘅競爭對手WhatsApp<br />\n佢地嘅網絡言論策略，<br />\n睇睇佢地多年來<br />\n每一次有競爭對手出現都會採用嘅戰略<br />\n<br />\n香港自2008年，<br />\n曾令WhatsApp產生危機感而有動作嘅<br />\n包括Line，WeChat，以及而家嘅Signal<br />\n<br />\n而每次，<br />\nWhatsApp所使用嘅策略都係同一套<br />\n包括淡化、抹黑、製造混亂<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp作為香港人慣性使用嘅通訊軟件<br />\n佢地無需要響網絡上贏出任何辯論<br />\n佢地嘅目的只有一個<br />\n就係「製造資訊疲勞」<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp非常清楚香港人<br />\n「怕麻煩」、「三分鐘熱度」特性<br />\n只要令大量資訊持續轟炸<br />\n（包括網絡上嘅罵戰，大量資訊湧現）<br />\n大部份網民都會響新鮮感下降<br />\n以及唔想再睇呢d情緒下<br />\n選擇繼續用返「慣性使用」嘅WhatsApp<br />\n<br />\n而事實亦證明，當年Line敗仗<br />\n係因為正、反、持平三方大混戰<br />\n大量網民對於資訊混亂無法理出頭緒或結論<br />\n最終選擇「唔轉會」，「用返WhatsApp算啦」<br />\n<br />\n而至於WeChat，<br />\n當年雖然有Big4廣告同演唱會聲勢浩大<br />\n甚至響海底隧道出口放出大型廣告牌，<br />\n聲勢一時無兩<br />\n但WhatsApp以遠低於廣告牌價錢<br />\n響討論區製造混亂<br />\n配合幾個討論區網民對大陸嘅反感<br />\n要維持WhatsApp於霸權實在易如反掌<br />\n<br />\n接下來，本人預計，<br />\nWhatsApp已經開始第一階段「淡化」手段<br />\n本港網絡上已經開始出現「Signal亦有問題」<br />\n以及「WhatsApp做法跟其他產品差不多<br />\n呢一類嘅講法<br />\n<br />\n稍後時間，高登連登等討論區，<br />\n將會出現大量有關Signal的不利新聞，<br />\n假新聞以及罵戰出現<br />\n呢一切響2月8日WhatsApp新Policy生效前<br />\n將會到達頂峰，令部份人跌落去<br />\n「算啦，Click同意WhatsApp嘅Policy」諗法<br />\n<br />\n假若各位真心唔希望霸權繼續<br />\n唔希望被PR公司左右，放棄你嘅私隱安全<br />\n請認清WhatsApp公司手段<br />\n並時刻保持初心，堅持到底<br />\n各位加油！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBy玻璃膠槍巴打<br />\n好奇問下 叫人轉用 signal個班del 晒wtsapp未？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aHPaeuV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aHPaeuV</a><br />\n#14 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BApksJS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBApksJS.jpg&h=4fa61c05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁當然有啲post唔排除係想認真討論<br />\n大家可以睇post之餘記得分析吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">希望大家保持初心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家睇到呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb131f7e96c75979376dd11e12e476ef35c14be6","tid":2363468,"uid":179645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:25:49.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7b56aa6ec5a6d28408f32439160e9e40da7e50","tid":2363468,"uid":179645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:26:34.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c238dbec6479f055ac37b7a1705893a458fc01a","tid":2363468,"uid":179645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:27:13.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60b552134b5c7268eee2c0b80b7c567ab44402e","tid":2363468,"uid":179645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca24f3199ad4612185dce7c72a666f0721fc739","tid":2363468,"uid":388108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:28:04